﻿<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

  <ItemGroup>

  </ItemGroup>
  <ItemGroup>
    <Content Include="favicon.ico">
      <CopyToOutputDirectory>Always</CopyToOutputDirectory>

  </ItemGroup>
  <ItemGroup>

  </ItemGroup>
  <ItemGroup>

  </ItemGroup>
</Project>
